<h1>China Held its Ground in 2012</h1>
<p><b>Shenzhen, China, January 15, 2013</b> - AsiaInspection, a leading provider of quality control services for businesses importing from Asia, today announces the AsiaInspection 2012 Q4 Barometer, offering a year in review of Asia-based manufacturing and the quality control services industry.</p>
<p>Here is a look back at a selection of the biggest <a href="/">manufacturing and quality control</a> industry-related stories of 2012.</p>
<h2 style="font-size:18px;">Asian Manufacturing in 2012: Despite Global Pessimism, Exports Remained Strong on Demand</h2>
